{"tid":653904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果承認 iPhone 7 升級 iOS 11.3 收音咪出現 bug","createTime":"2018-05-05T06:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T16:56:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"977549b6e93c46a6ead758e15119bc0edde4e109","tid":653904,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:54:05.000Z","msg":"最近，蘋果向美國網絡確認 iOS 11.3 出現另一個會影響 iPhone 通話質素的 bug。<br />\n<br />\n包括 Macrumors、9to5Mac 在內多個美國科技網站收到聲稱是蘋果授權維修商的內部文件，說蘋果得知部分 iPhone 7 和 iPhone 7 Plus 用戶在升級 iOS 11.3 之後收音咪失靈，無法在通話時使用「擴音」功能甚至令收音咪無法運作。蘋果要求授權維修商在維修客戶 iPhone 前先要求客人移除連接耳機或其他音響裝置，去檢查 iPhone 的收音咪是否能正常操作。<br />\n<br />\n在檢查期間如果發現利用 iPhone 通話無法擴音或收音咪失靈，授權維修商就要為 iPhone 進行音效診斷，如果發現「裝置不能連接」或者「元件並不支援」的情況，授權維修商就會維修 iPhone。如果受收音咪問題影響的 iPhone 7 和 iPhone 7 Plus 過保，授權維修商可以向蘋果發出豁免要求，雖然蘋果文件沒有提及免費，但似乎可以讓授權維修商酌情處理，包括免費更換 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/05/iphone-7-ios-11-3-microphone-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2Fiphone-7-ios-11-3-microphone-bug%2F&d=ZrrFDRUuioFNkS1lvnVcl10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5c3038e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/05/iphone-7-ios-11-3-microphone-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"c90d164ada33412e9b8194e20e1780ea13eb6bd9","tid":653904,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"apple已死"},{"pid":"3785446a4a4f6bbd5d00ad6ae977d1e6466b512b","tid":653904,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c5c142c5cd1ca007a2b4d1eb9fb8f93ef5e87298","tid":653904,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3c0f4eff87dee46a6437ce82e80e9be6c1bf90c1","tid":653904,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d92c889615f37346f9f08b4bbff4d6eb